// Copy this file to `arduino_secrets.h` in the same directory, then replace
// the placeholder key with your real key. The real `arduino_secrets.h` is
// gitignored so your secrets never leave your machine.
//
// The key MUST be identical to the key in mailbox_sender/arduino_secrets.h
// and in mailbox_receiver/arduino_secrets.h — all three devices share one PSK.

